('11','0','10','保定——虎山：寻找金钱源头之旅','','','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    <img src=\"/uploads/2016/0331/c37ae22c9406537c6524d6170be02c29.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虎山，位于保定市西部，曲阳县最北部，因其山顶的一块巨石颇似蓄势待发的猛虎而得名。与著名的古北岳恒山相连，主峰“三尖梁”海拔1300多米，由于与唐县、阜平接壤，形成了“一脚踩三县”的山岳旅游景观，景区面积达20多平方公里。</p><div id=\"img53295071\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"53295071|2569650\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"53295071\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"53295071|36483328\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"http://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M03/A2/C0/CggYG1XrqOGAUMu7AA3joK-xK1A269_C_671_10000.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M03/A2/C0/CggYG1XrqOGAUMu7AA3joK-xK1A269_C_671_10000.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5) 50% 50% no-repeat;\" height=\"377\" width=\"671\"/></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    虎山，一直深藏于太行山中，峰峦起伏，多年来人迹罕至，自然生态保持了原汁原味。山中气候湿润，空气异常清新纯净，细雾蒸腾，迷蒙如雨，似着上轻旅纱衣，被游人誉为大自然的“天然氧吧”。黄羊、松鼠、各种鸟类等野生动物不时出没于山间。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><div id=\"img53295742\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"53295742|2569650\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"53295742\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"53295742|36483328\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"http://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M03/A5/47/CggYHlXrqaSAPuo1ABzywK93uZU735_C_671_10000.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M03/A5/47/CggYHlXrqaSAPuo1ABzywK93uZU735_C_671_10000.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5) 50% 50% no-repeat;\" height=\"377\" width=\"671\"/></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    山中叮咚作响的“金水泉”奏响了虎山一曲天然之歌。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><div id=\"img53295956\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"53295956|2569650\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"53295956\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"53295956|36483328\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/A5/77/CggYHVXrqlyAXcdvABnrBUTsobY497_C_671_10000.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/A5/77/CggYHVXrqlyAXcdvABnrBUTsobY497_C_671_10000.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5) 50% 50% no-repeat;\" height=\"1192\" width=\"671\"/></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    淘金文化，作为虎山景区的主题定位，也是虎山的特色之一。在全国体现淘金文化的景区独此一家，这也形成了虎山景区的特色之处。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><div id=\"img53296337\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"53296337|2569650\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"53296337\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"53296337|36483328\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/9B/C2/CggYGlXrqs6AOuPeABaIEnd8gcU413_C_671_10000.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/9B/C2/CggYGlXrqs6AOuPeABaIEnd8gcU413_C_671_10000.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5) 50% 50% no-repeat;\" height=\"1192\" width=\"671\"/></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    “淘金洞”是古淘金洞遗留下的洞穴，深达几百米的洞穴就有多处。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans G