?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/17/03/CggYGVXfJJeAf1yiABGPzKDEiaE363_C_350_234.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/17/03/CggYGVXfJJeAf1yiABGPzKDEiaE363_C_350_234.jpg\" height=\"234\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px; height: 280px;\"/><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>九门口水上长城<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52730347\" class=\"w_img \" data-likeid=\"52730347|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52730347\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52730347|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: auto; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M02/16/A7/CggYG1XfJnqAWfq5ACP-Ic55DvQ397_R_10000_500.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M02/16/A7/CggYG1XfJnqAWfq5ACP-Ic55DvQ397_R_10000_500.jpg\" height=\"500\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px;\"/><p class=\"description\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">往前走就是长城，左手是隧道，因为姥姥姥爷所以我们不爬山，先隧道走起</p><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>九门口水上长城<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">明代以前，一片石是一条京--秦之间的交通要道。到了明洪武十三年，著名将领徐达奉旨修筑九门口段长城，竣工后，徐达大将军和设计师们根据九门口所处的险要地理位置，设计开掘出一条从长城内侧校军场，不经九门城关，而秘密直通关外的山中暗道，这条坐落在长城下面山体中的暗道全长1027米。<br/><br/>隧道共有两个出口，一个入口。一个出口直对点将台，一个出口为一片石战场。一个出口直通关外，洞内有29个大小岩洞，分别为号钟室、卫生间(茅房)、禁闭室&nbsp;、中军室、水牢、存粮库、伙房、水井房、碾房、兵器室、练功房、炮室、刑具展室、驻军室、佛室、关公和山神祭拜室等洞室，暗道中既可以屯兵又可由内城突发奇兵至攻城之敌后部如神兵天降，暗道中可以驻扎约2000人，洞内设计了排水系统和通风孔以保证驻扎在洞室中的士兵活动自由，洞内的水井清澈见底水质甘甜清冽，可供2000余人饮用。<br/><br/>一六四四年，李自成农民起义军攻占北京后，分兵长途奔袭夹击山海关。首先在内侧攻占九门城关，吴三桂所引多尔滚清军在关外久攻不下，抓住一名原明代守城军士，探到暗道位置，遂派奇兵由暗道外面直扑城内，形成了内外夹击之势，终使长途奔袭的农民军败北，这就是历史上有名的&quot;一片石大战&quot;，最终以清军的胜利宣告结束。&nbsp;长城古暗道现已被辟为旅游景点，当您参观完长城之后，再到&quot;城中城&quot;之称的长城隧道中浏览一番，当别有情趣。</p><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52730197\" class=\"w_img \" data-likeid=\"52730197|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52730197\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52730197|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: auto; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg06.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M02/17/0B/CggYGVXfJlSAIgOQABZDh_Tq9Zw013_R_10000_500.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg06.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M02/17/0B/CggYGVXfJlSAIgOQABZDh_Tq9Zw013_R_10000_500.jpg\" height=\"500\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px;\"/><p class=\"description\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">穿过卖卖街道</p><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial