 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>前所古城<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">门票；免费<br/>前所镇南临渤海，北枕燕山余脉，扼守着关内外交通要道的辽西走廊，号称关外第一所城，是明代建制的126座关隘军镇所城之一，经常驻有数千人的屯军，是目前全国唯一保存完整的一座所城。<br/>方方正正的古城墙，东西南北各有1里地的长度。前所镇的古城墙独特之处是它只有东南西三个城门，而没有北门。东门叫定远门，南门叫广定门，西门叫永望门。<br/>东面的城墙已年久失修而风化坍塌得破败不堪，且杂草从生，南面和西面的城墙正在修复，尚存的西门瓮城已经修复的焕然一新，北城墙被众多临街店铺所遮挡。<br/>我们从东门进，走十字街，漫步在古城的大街小巷，出南门，走上强流河河畔，再进入西门瓮城，登上西门，再环顾古城前所的城里城外，清澈的强流河从城西蜿蜒流过，石块堆沏齐整的河岸上，草木青葱。城里仅有的东南西北四条小街，把古城分割得井然有序。小街两旁，满目都是几十年前的老式平房，青砖灰瓦，多少显得陈旧和破落。</p><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52730112\" class=\"w_img img_divide img_fl\" data-likeid=\"52730112|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52730112\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52730112|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 420px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; float: left; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M03/18/FB/CggYHVXfKFeAeMGwAAwzMM-6Y_s183_C_350_234.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M03/18/FB/CggYHVXfKFeAeMGwAAwzMM-6Y_s183_C_350_234.jpg\" height=\"234\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px; height: 280px;\"/><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>前所古城<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div><div id=\"img52730307\" class=\"w_img img_divide img_fr\" data-likeid=\"52730307|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52730307\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52730307|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 420px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; float: right; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M00/19/2D/CggYHFXfKF6AT35AAA3FVbQahwU867_C_350_234.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M00/19/2D/CggYHFXfKF6AT35AAA3FVbQahwU867_C_350_234.jpg\" height=\"234\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px; height: 280px;\"/><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>前所古城<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">据旧《省志》记载，前所镇在商代属孤竹国，周封天下，此地为幽州地。春秋战国燕王经略辽西，此地归附于燕国的版图。秦统天下，划州为郡县，幽州成为了辽西郡。汉承秦制，在这里置海阳县，东汉沿用西汉建制。此后历朝在这里或置郡或设县，到了明代，在这里设卫建所，前所之名沿用至今。<br/><br/>　　前所古镇城西有条强流河，蜿蜒清澈，绕城而过。强流河河宽百米，最深处七八米，发源于前所镇北部牛羊村的扑庄子，流经牛羊村的狼洞子，再经大柳村的白家窝棚、何家村的吴家庄、前所古城西门外、杨家村的楼屯、杨屯，最后注入渤海，全长15000米。此河原名急水河，传说清代乾隆皇帝东巡路过此地，随同而来的上千匹马一起饮水，河水竟没有断流，乾隆赞叹说：“此河乃强流也。”之后人们将此河改名为强流河。前所镇附近还有一条河流叫洪流河，其宽度和深度与强流河不相上下，注入渤海，全长6000米。强流河沿岸以及东北侧有大片的树林，郁郁苍苍，风景秀丽，环境优美，被称为前所镇的天然水上公园。<br/><br/>　　前所镇城基本呈正方形，长、宽约500米，墙高10米，设置三个城门，没有北门。北边城墙上建真武庙，毁于战火，现已不存。东、西、南三门上以前都有题匾，东门曰定远，南门曰广定，西门曰永望，北面嵌石匾，刻有“中前所”三个字。各城门原建有瓮城，现唯有西门瓮城尚存。城内十字街口北侧，原有钟鼓楼一座，因年久失修已经塌陷，1958年，被全部拆毁。<br/><br/>　　前所镇党委副书记李方起说，前所古城是关外第一所城，坐落于辽西走廊纽带区域，这座明代古城在102国道与强流河交汇处，南濒大海，北依燕山，扼辽西走廊西端，是连接关内外交通的咽喉要道，也是山海关外第一道屏障。</p><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52730108\" class=\"w_img \" data-likeid=\"52730108|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52730108\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52730108|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: auto; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M05/0F/FC/CggYGlXfKAqAE4i8AAxv8_Qf8L4954_R_10000_500.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M05/0F/FC/CggYGlXfKAqAE4i8AAxv8_Qf8L4954_R_10000_500.jpg\" height=\"500\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px;\"/><p class=\"description\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">数百年来，前所古城饱经战火洗礼，也历尽人间繁华。如今漫步于古城的大街小巷中，触目皆是的青砖旧瓦，恍如隔世，荒芜的野草枯败于城头，风化的砖石倾诉岁月回声</p><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>前所古城<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">前所镇因是战守之地，与之相关的歌咏诗作也连篇累牍，其中最有名的是乾隆皇帝谱写的御制诗《过中前所》：“峰堡冈台每相望，耗民无救坠明纲。椓人久擅杀生柄，怯将徒称守御方。极目一时警跸路，回思此地战征场。动关心惧仔肩重，祖业维艰刻敢忘。&nbsp;”乾隆以此诗总结了明亡的教训，告诫皇族子弟要时刻牢记祖辈创业之艰辛，守业之任重。</p></div><div class=\"ctd_content wtd_content\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 40px 10px 14px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto;\"><ul class=\"daytitle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><li><p>第5天</p></li><li><p><span class=\"time\">2015-08-27</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">相传故事发生在江浙地区的一个小村庄。孟家老汉因搭救了一窝小燕儿，燕儿报恩，给老汉送来一刻葫芦籽，老汉种下葫芦，藤却爬到隔壁姜家，在姜家院里结了一个葫芦。姜家只有一孤寡妇人，见到葫芦就和孟老汉商量，赶到秋天葫芦长成，一家一半做个水瓢。孟老汉也答应了，谁想到没等做瓢，葫芦成熟便自己裂开，葫芦里倒是个小姑娘。孟姜两家均无子女，姜老太手快，一把抱过孩子想占为己有，孟老汉不依，两家争执不休。经人调解，两家共同抚养孩子，姑娘取名孟姜女。后来孟姜女长大，与一逃难的小伙结婚。结果好日子不长，婚后不久，小伙儿便被秦皇捉去修长城。到了冬天，孟姜女思念丈夫，便带了寒衣北上寻夫。到了山海关才知道，丈夫已死，尸首被埋在长城下，孟姜女痛哭不止，哭倒了长城八百里，终于尸骨露出地面，经仙人指点，孟姜女用滴血认亲的方法找到丈夫尸骨，为其下葬。同时她的美貌让秦王垂涎，欲纳其为妃。孟姜女借口坐船出海游玩儿，当远离海岸时，孟姜女举身入海殉情而死。顷刻间狂风大作，秦王不得已退至海湾躲避，风浪过后，秦始皇感念海湾旧自己一命，为海湾赐名止锚湾，此时海中孟姜女落水处升起巨石，大的如孟姜女的身形，小的如包裹寒衣的包袱。百姓感念孟姜女殉情壮举，就称这碣石为孟姜女墓。在水文学上，此从秦皇岛至此的这段海域被称作碣石地貌，万里长城的起点老龙头也在此海域。</p><div id=\"poi4509632\" class=\"poi_title\" title=\"碣石\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px; line-height: 35px; padding: 30px 0px 10px;\"><span class=\"g_sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 32px; height: 35px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 10px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0px -116px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>碣石</div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">时间很快，4天就要结束了，感恩我的家人如此疼我，爱我，给我一个幸福的假期</p></div><p><br/></p>','/uploads/2016/0331/79b447c929ec228d3a88ede7df3c15f1.jpg','1459238249','1459406991','25','','','','50','',NULL,'21,31',NULL,NULL,'','0',NULL,'','追溯秦汉文化之根，东戴河是中国最早的皇家海洋','0','','','10','50');-- <xjx> --
