('21','0','20','【回顾】草原天路自驾二日游归来','','','','一起流年','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">    <img src=\"/uploads/2016/0331/30d5d207ace5ea64bf59b5e2e0b1d649.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" align=\"left\"/>​</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    9月12日，车加车网俱乐部跟大家一起去张北看了天路的秋景，一路上我们看着天路美丽的景色，很充实，也很辛苦。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    　　在此之前，我们虽未见过，但我们以真诚的心相待，收获了友谊，也收获了快乐。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    　　感谢这次天路自驾游的每位参与者和祝福我们的人，有你们的支持，相信以后我们会做的更好！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-