('22','0','21','【回顾】许亭水库小聚归来','','','','一起流年','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">      \n    9月20日车加车网俱乐部进行了一次小聚会，地点在许亭水库。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">   \n    首先感谢参与本次活动的各位车友，感谢你们对我们的认可，因为各种原因，本次活动没把大家照顾好，反而大家还要帮我们烧烤，谢谢梅子、SUV军团、暗夜精灵、-停、蓝沧海……辛苦大家。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    对大家给予我们的帮助表示感谢，真的谢谢你们。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,