('32','0','31','扒一扒没有PS过的凤凰古城','','','','烟雨霏霏','<p>大多数现在的年青人都有2个小小的梦想“一次说走就走的旅行和一场奋不顾身的爱情”，我也不能免俗，在看了无数凤凰古城的皂片之后，约了几个小伙伴就立刻定下了行程。</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0331/aaa25e5dc24e6f4b9b366f62bab21f91.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><p>去凤凰没有直达的飞机也没有直达的火车，所以不管选择哪一条线路，貌似都要在路上耽搁一天时间。</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/0f3d7214321ae85f9665395ca97ceaaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>既然要耽搁这么久，不吃饱了哪能行！于是我们先到长沙，吃饱了毛爷爷最喜欢的红烧肉，包了一辆车，出发~</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/2ef5c66354a5423944dd116c575a68ea.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>要出去玩怎么能不养好精神呢，在车上大睡一觉之后，一睁眼就到了古城。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/926fe380a7478965daf55e044c8a2b3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>在凤凰古城下道的时候，高速的执法警察突然拦下我们的车。</p><p>我们第一反应是，难道我们车上有人犯事了，谁？！是谁？！！</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/215965ec79447f3a68be87c4953f751a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>赶紧摇下车窗，一脸诚惶诚恐等待训话。没想到警察特客气的跟我们说，可以到我家去坐坐，我家在古城里面开客栈的，今天特价！</p><p>这都可以？警察拉客！</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/046e69a39f3ce0fcf12af2a0e8ebf789.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>听说湘西人民匪气略重，怎么地，还没进门呢就被镇住了。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/65e0ceb69b276a087cb66c97c6a76ac0.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>开了一天车终于到了凤凰古城，虽说是古城，但是没有城门只有售票处，我也是醉了。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/0f8cdc15e401bac946ff6e59036e167d.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>先上张夜景给大家看看，美的不要不要的~</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/38ac54aebea8ba3daf44a1db1a8f28c6.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>这里要到重点内容了——“晚上十一点半以后的凤凰古城是不需要检票的，而夜景在十二点钟才关闭，也就是说23：30-24：00之间的半小时，我们是可以在景区里面畅通无阻的！”有这等好事岂能错过，立刻扔下行李我们就奔向了景区。（此处应有皂片）</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/252b5d95feceb271e046752126606e23.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>愿还没许好，先放了几个小花灯凑凑热闹~晚上看这些小灯灰常漂亮~白天就是一片一片烂纸漂在河面上，那场面简直不忍直视！</p><p>为了大家心中那点美好的古城形象，照片就不放了，大家还是看夜景吧。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/68c82f2f9539829c51aae3951720d480.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>凤凰的晚上让人觉得很惬意。石板路、吊脚楼、河岸凉风习习，两岸的小酒吧带着些许魅惑的味道。都说成都是艳遇之都，夜晚的凤凰又何尝不是呢。</p><p>旖旎灯光，缠绵垂柳，耳畔传来不知是谁的歌声。</p><p>不艳遇都对不起自己！！可惜朋友看的太紧。。。艳遇都被打散了。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/80a22da92ae3e02a068dbe30f22080b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>凤凰是在太美啦，激动得我5点半就醒了起来梳妆打扮，心里想着，反正都到这里了，觉什么时候睡都行，来了就要使劲玩~立马把所有的小伙伴全部叫起来~</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/0104ac9ccdd1e27f20fe51b745a30645.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>起来就有点后悔，白天就应该好好睡觉，晚上再逛古城！！</p><p>昨天晚上看到的风景明明是这样的，灯火辉煌~</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/376a4848d0ad49db45b7d391d31a0b09.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>白天两边看见的却是这样的：</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/07ad81f916da85377225d84a1c335bfb.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>什么情况这是？几个意思啊？？晚上那些缠绵悱恻的灯光呢？？？</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/73ee6946010c7fa8c532578c0b8692ae.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>来前看了很多古城的皂片，那叫一个美，绝对的仙境！但现实却把人从天堂打入地狱。</p><p>水边的高塔皂片中是这样的：</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/a28fd679a7fa90723e01e75da40080be.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>走到跟前一看却是这样：</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/0ece59dd1a8c4a3b60200b8efba17a5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>明明是凤凰古城，这搞得和建筑工地似得，这是要闹哪样。不好看是一说，这连个护栏都没有，万一掉下去，这就真跟古城融为一体再也分不开了啊~</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/26f8a476b83fd1ebeceb2f179cf400b0.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>路边废弃的金属</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/f57c0e18b4b14bd3d2e92308fe43f1fd.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>古道中干活的工人</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/005dfa211bb77b6e0e6c345afefb1da8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>好吧，这些都能PS，角度不同拍出的效果也就不同，我认了！可是！！可是！！！</p><p>没走两步就有人拉着要拍照！！！</p><p>而且，不管你同意不同意，人家都会大咧咧的给你照下来，你是我什么人啊就给我照！</p><p>照相也就算了，照完还拉着非要十块钱再卖给你。那人说了句“笑一个，照得不好看的话，留下来当压寨夫人！”尼玛，差点吓尿了。</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/1280ff40c766eb5fa7971d000be7c386.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>早就听说路边会有唱歌要钱的小孩子和老婆婆。坐船前还真看见了，不见不知道，一见吓一跳。</p><p>原来这是真的！不管你听不听，人家就在那唱！</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/85497723df660126dcf8c28ce6efbc88.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>纯粹是一路追着你唱着要钱~阿姨，我要自己赚学费呢！</p><p>最坑的还是个老奶奶，拉住我们要钱，最后给了几块钱才说了声谢谢走开！这真是颇有土匪风范~</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/91a899d1294a66ea3251ff96776990b4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>几分钟后坐船到了苗人谷的路口，走上去就是苗寨，在牛头大门前要对歌，不过在车上唐阿妹已经教了我们两首，没问题。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/953abf3b87ff34814dabba2b0a08ff32.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>有趣的是我们后面那个团这样唱也行：（两只老虎的调）肚子饿了，肚子饿了，要吃饭，要吃饭，随便来点小菜，随便来点小酒，就行啦，就行啦。我们当场被雷倒。</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/cba98d03fbe33ffc90199accee6cca9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>沱江两岸，虹桥边，没走几步就能看到卖着各式小吃的摊子或店家，当地着名的臭豆腐、香豆腐、姜糖、炸小鱼螃蟹丶血粑鸭丶凉粉，酸萝卜、酸钢豆，麻辣炸罐巴、炸糯米辣、苗族竹筒饭丶回族羊肉串丶糖炒栗子等等。好吃的太多了，真想在古城里走到哪吃到哪~</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/f9af0ba49a462a6ce42679ec7d8ec374.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>凤凰是小吃的荟萃之地，各种各样的小吃多到数不胜数。</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/3096642632dfeff7abc004321105e94e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p>不过在路边发现各种XX粑粑的食物还是要非常注意的，这个味道。终身难忘啊！那个酸爽。。。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0401/a03d025316d3517755b37a3b7ca15d46.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>传说中的古镇手工制品店玲琅满目，可是看这个款式，啧啧~怎么感觉这么眼熟呢？</p><p>想问一句，店家，您在某宝是不是开了N多分店？</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0401/0fc622b0c7db5e9168cf4040d196d806.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><p>　　吃也吃了，玩也玩了，要是凤凰赶紧修好了，水赶紧弄干净了，“土匪”们也不再随便拦路要钱拉人了，手工制品不再从义乌小商品市场进货了，这里还是凤凰还是很美好哒！</p><p>　　曾经的古城可能没有现在这么多商业气息，晚上也没有这么多灯光耀眼，名气大了，人也多了，各种购物需求随之而来。不能说不好，也算不上好吧。</p><p>　　古城的景色也算迷人，少一些人造，多一些自然，想必会比现在更加讨人喜欢！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p>','/uploads/2016/0331/aaa25e5dc24e6f4b9b366f62bab21f91.jpg','1459241303','1464921577','24','','','',NULL,'湘西土家族苗族自治州',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','1',NULL,'','大多数现在的年青人都有2个小小的梦想“一次说走就走的旅行和一场奋不顾身的爱情”，我也不能免俗','0','','','10','0');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_article` VALUES
('33','0','32','人间仙境——喀纳斯','','','','烟雨霏霏','<p>喀纳斯湖（英语：Kanas Lake）位于中国新疆阿勒泰地区布尔津县北部，是一个内陆淡水湖，湖水来自奎屯、友谊峰等山的冰川融水和当地降水，湖面海拔1374米，面积45.73㎞²，湖水最深处达188.5米左右，蓄水量达53.8亿立方米。</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0331/08d0182f1b2dbde8ef4857e2b1ec9f82.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><p>喀纳斯湖位于新疆阿勒泰地区，是第四纪冰川作用形成的高山淡水湖泊。湖泊、雪山、草原、白桦林、牧场、河流、民族风情组成一幅色彩斑斓的美丽画卷，被誉为“东方瑞士、摄影师天堂”。2009年被《中国国家地理》杂志评为“中国最美湖泊”。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0331/975cac883a9d9bd70b2e9b36512cda00.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>喀纳斯湖外形呈月牙，湖区景观主要有驼颈湾、变色湖、卧龙湾等；生长有哲罗鲑、细鳞鲑等珍稀鱼类。</p><p><img src=\"http://ly.chejiache.com/uploads/2016/0331/405aaa5735d138c937331dd773232180.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p>喀纳斯湖是第四纪冰川作用形成的高山湖泊，2009年被《中国国家地理》杂志评为“中国最美湖泊”。</p><p><br/></p>','/uploads/2016/0331/08d0182f1b2dbde8ef4857e2b1ec9f82.jpg','1459416175','1464921929','82','','','',NULL,'新疆阿勒泰',NULL,'17',NULL,NULL,'','0',NULL,'','喀纳斯湖（英语：Kanas Lake）位于中国新疆阿勒泰地区布尔津县北部，是一个内陆淡水湖，湖水来自奎屯','0','','','10','0');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_article` VALUES
('34','0','33','清凉一夏，梦幻驼梁游','','','','飒飒','<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 21pt;\"><br/></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 21pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">眼瞅着夏天就这么到来了，气温也一天天升高起来，&nbsp;总想找个地方避暑纳凉，逃离这高温湿热的“火炉”城市！早就听朋友们说起驼梁，说那里景色如何如何美，空气如何如何清新，尤其是气温如何如何低。总之，驼梁是如何如何好！于</span><span style=\"line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">是动心决定亲自去体验一下这个所谓”凉都“之凉。在朋友的鼓动之下，决定利用周末时间亲自一探究竟。赶在五月份的最后一个周末，约上死党，两人一辆车，开始了这次清凉的一晚两日自驾游。</span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 21pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/a949846fb4e1689a7b76176687ea4171.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"44423\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"32290\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top-width: 2.5px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 2px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(235, 103, 148); overflow: hidden; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-bcless=\"darken\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(229, 58, 116); box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(235, 103, 148);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">驾车路线</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-top-width: 32px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); border-right-width: 32px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 2px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">石家庄—56Km（S071）—岗南收费站—6Km（S202）—苏家庄—21Km（G207）—寨头乡—23Km（S201）—漫山桥—22Km（S201）—驼梁<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"32290\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top-width: 2.5px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 2px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(235, 103, 148); overflow: hidden; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-bcless=\"darken\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(229, 58, 116); box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(235, 103, 148);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">山的征程</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-top-width: 32px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); border-right-width: 32px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 2px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">过于兴奋，早上很早就醒来了，七点和朋友正式踏上了征途，大约十点到达目的地——驼梁，此时的山脚下已经停了不少车辆。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/6ec0621f9661d10578f4c9c15ff0613a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">驼梁所在的村子叫做前大地村，这里家家户户都开农家院，所以住宿不成问题，周末房价自然要贵些，标间价格大约在</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">150</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">—</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">大洋左右，也可以凭借自己的三寸不烂之舌与店家讨价还价，最终我们以</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">130</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">块钱成功预定一晚的标间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">当然，如果你对住的要求比较高，且银子又比较充足的话，可以住宾馆，价格从</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">300</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">元到</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">500</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">元不等，条件肯定要比农家院好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">住宿搞定，稍作休息，店家热情地为我们介绍中午的饭食，种类还真不少，荤菜、肉菜、粥、汤等都有，我们着急爬山，随便吃了一点零食，便开始奔向大山。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">驼梁景区的门票为</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">65</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">元一张，去之前可在各旅游网站提前预定，价格会稍微便宜一些。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">不多说，先上图，满足一下各位看官的好奇心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/c3c14dfe84acc9d302376b2616b21a74.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/a491d0da8a9021ecf37d455b402bbf1f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">驼梁景区主要由三叠泉景区、云顶草原、百瀑峡景区组成，三者组成一个闭合的环线。若你是懒癌者，想乘缆车上山，可选择三叠泉进入。我们想挑战一下自己，于是选择由百瀑峡方向右行上山。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/cd4e408d43794aec660ad162f09e95cb.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/e1cddcb4b38dc09b68997622fb7393aa.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">驼梁景区的主要特色是水！这里水量很充沛，到处都能看见泉水，一直伴随到接近山顶的红桦林。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/5463f62552c8fa380a619002f2a70f26.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">由于雨水充沛，空气湿度很大，树木和石头上都是苔藓，绿绿的，好可耐呦。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/75d01d4238548bde181abe46c840bc3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">景区内古木参天，森林覆盖率非常高，人行其间，只能从树叶的缝隙中看见蓝天白云。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/407572477f1341716d53118e5d365aff.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">由于空气质量好，坡度也比较缓，所以爬山并不累，边走边欣赏美景边拍照。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px;\">看到路边的小野花，实在忍不住，摘下来戴在自己的头上，好像回到了童年。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/870b07acf963e4022fe09cbe9ac082fb.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\">接近山顶的松树林很密实，阳光从树缝中透过，路上树影斑驳，很有意境。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/f910d9448a803e1fef28ee79e827a29e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/2fd18be7cc9b23e89bfd0530bca0140e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">穿过接近山顶的松树林，前面就可看到蓝天白云了，云顶草原就在眼前！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">视野突然变得很开阔，一大片被围栏挡起来的草原呈现在眼前，太美了！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/732fb55ac6dd2f887f00cdd9fdda4d06.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/2d3cc2c9819d7213324f63069c4f7cbc.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\">由于海拔较高，不适合树木生长，各种野花野草便成为这里的主角，虽不娇艳，但更显质朴。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/db79474050069fbc42e0968a31b4542f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/177bd5642a48d5150ca6e3e6f1b1cfc6.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\">云顶草原上好多人都在野餐，我们也打开背包，坐在草地上开始了野餐，好好吃耶。酒足饭饱，在草原略作停留，继续向驼梁主峰进发！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/13410d0c5f497711a2f1994516006517.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\">终于到山顶了，很激动，突然想到了一首歌曲“终于等到你，还好我没有放弃。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/fc0403c595033ecaf88b8862b207cf45.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\">山顶空气很清新，视野很开阔，山风吹过，舒服极了！通往五岳寨的步行栈道，很美！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/6bf3a5c19668627df6a59f55310b17d3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">爬上将近3000米高的山峰，还是有点累的，腿酸得不要不要的，真是佩服那些爬上来的大叔大妈们。趁还有一点力气在，赶紧下山咯！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">下山的时候实在是没有力气来拍照片了，寥寥几张而已。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/fce0d382dcab167162c97715690fabfa.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/09a3590abf0c5a38f43751632d5ec4af.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\">下到缆车处，终究抵挡不过缆车的诱惑，两人一拍即合，兴奋地坐上了缆车（单程50元/人，双程90元/人），哈哈哈！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/fff83e6c187374f7356ad61c1c830cbe.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">终于下到山脚，累屎宝宝了，赶紧走回旅馆。恰赶上老板娘做饭，我们两个人点了一荤两宿，外加包子和汤，很普通的一顿家常饭，花了我们将近100块钱，稍微有点小贵，可以理解，毕竟是在景区。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">老板娘的拿手菜——农家小炒肉，还是蛮不错的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/90ff1dc18efbac96276d36f3524cc45a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">一般农家院都是会提供饭食的，若不想在农家院吃，村子里、山脚下有不少小吃馆、饭店等，价格高低不等，看自己喜好咯，想吃点啥就吃点啥吧。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"32290\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top-width: 2.5px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 2px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(235, 103, 148); overflow: hidden; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-bcless=\"darken\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(229, 58, 116); box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(235, 103, 148);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">漂流</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-top-width: 32px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(235, 103, 148); border-right-width: 32px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 2px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">晚上的驼梁还是有些凉的，现在去需要盖厚被子。山里空气好，又逢晴天，看星星、赏月亮、谈理想，悠哉游哉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0pt; line-height: 21pt; text-indent: 0pt;\">一觉睡到自然醒，第二天起来决定去附近的漂流谷漂流(90元/人)一番再回程。一定要记得带上换洗衣服，会湿透的呦。</span></p></section><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 21pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">大家都玩得好开森！</span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 21pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/a86c9246ff43b176adcd63de03562841.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 21pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">到达漂流终点，浑身上下都湿透了，赶紧到旁边的小棚子里去换了干衣服。</span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 21pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\">我们的驼梁二日游到此结束，开车回庄，心中大声呐喊“我还会回来的！”</span></p><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; font-size: 14px;\"><br/><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>','/uploads/2016/0530/a949846fb4e1689a7b76176687ea4171.jpg','1464572433','1464921456','195','','','',NULL,'驼梁',NULL,'16',NULL,NULL,'','0',NULL,'','...','0','','','10','0');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_article` VALUES
('35','0','34','沙漠于海洋的吻痕——翡翠岛','','','','翡翠','<section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\" data-id=\"3238\" data-color=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" data-custom=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(33, 33, 34); margin: 2em auto 1em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"line-height: 1.4; margin-right: 10px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"border: 28px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); border-image-source: url(http://remote.wx135.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei95cVZBcW9adkRpYkZPTWlhdWlibE5SeFV6WWxNR0RxRTNDT2xZdjBOZ1h4bTBYOWJUWDZSYjNLYnl1NVlPV09oaWNVSnZsV3o2N2liUk9JZWFOalNKMWJMRFp3LzA=); border-image-slice: 28; margin-top: 1em; color: rgb(33, 33, 34); line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"135brush\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\">在河北的昌黎有一处可以让你左手大海，右手绿洲，中间沙漠的奇景。 它的名字叫翡翠岛。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\" data-id=\"85850\"><section style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"line-height: 2em; color: inherit; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/06776dc078d45f2dd2af9b74dab256a2.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; color: inherit; white-space: normal; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">据传由天空鸟瞰，这里海水的颜色反射出翠绿色，半岛三面环海，被包裹其中，故取名“翡翠岛”。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: -1px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><br/></p></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\" data-id=\"85850\"><section style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"line-height: 2em; color: inherit; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/b946797aeb4a8daae4c83ee663cb97ea.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; color: inherit; white-space: normal; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\">“翡，赤羽雀也；翠，青羽雀也”。翡翠，以它的深邃晶莹的质地，蕴涵着神秘东方的灵秀之气，古往今来不知引诱了多少人，而用这样充满了灵气的名字去命名渤海湾上的一个半岛，又是多么惹人遐思！</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: -1px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\" data-id=\"85850\"><section style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"line-height: 2em; color: inherit; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0530/390da76efb5989879f296d62fca3913f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; color: inherit; white-space: normal; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\">岛上沙山连绵起伏，陡缓交错，线条流畅，造型优美，最高处达44米，方圆7平方公里，素有“京东大沙漠”之称。一半沙漠一半海水，景色漂亮奇幻，这里是沙漠与大海的吻痕。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: -1px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\" data-id=\"85850\"><section style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px; box-sizing: bo